393
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:38,120
Oh, damn it.

394
00:13:43,140 --> 00:13:43,660
Clip.

395
00:13:43,840 --> 00:13:44,520
Pass it over.

396
00:13:45,460 --> 00:13:46,060
What's left?

397
00:13:46,060 --> 00:13:47,580
Just finishing the M6.

398
00:13:47,680 --> 00:13:48,940
Put the slide back on the frame.

