Should have told her, Jim.

406
00:14:01,400 --> 00:14:01,880
Yeah.

407
00:14:04,700 --> 00:14:08,620
Sooner or later, life gets the drop on you, kid.

408
00:14:09,780 --> 00:14:10,160
Mom?

409
00:14:12,820 --> 00:14:13,300
Bang.

410
00:14:18,820 --> 00:14:21,620
Your dress is very pink.

411
00:14:22,620 --> 00:14:23,320
Thank you.

412
00:14:23,640 --> 00:14:26,000
Your uniform is very crisp.

413
00:14:26,660 --> 00:14:31,900
Uh, so Jason, my friend who doesn't want to wreck your cousin's life, says you work at

