00:15:01,680 --> 00:15:02,220
Yes, sir.

428
00:15:03,380 --> 00:15:04,740
What in the world?

429
00:15:05,300 --> 00:15:06,640
Sorry to interrupt everyone's dinner.

430
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:07,940
But I have an announcement.

431
00:15:09,380 --> 00:15:12,980
I've just gotten word that the fleet base at Reach, the covenant,

