00:15:47,420 --> 00:15:49,360
I like your old school binash, I'm afraid.

449
00:15:49,900 --> 00:15:50,740
You wanted a meeting.

450
00:15:51,020 --> 00:15:53,380
What are you doing nosing around the apocalypse?

